    • Method Detail

      • getSuggestedFeatureNames

        List<String> getSuggestedFeatureNames(String query,
                                      int maxResults)
        Searches for geographic features by name, returning the names of the closest n matches. Intended for use by an autocomplete widget.
        Parameters:
        query - search term
        maxResults - maximum number of results to return
        Returns:
        list of names found

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        the feature if found, otherwise null
